{
  "texts": [
    "Their results surpass those of LineVul and other DL-based SDD methods across multiple evaluation metrics.",
    "However, due to the limitations of the UniXcoder in the pre-training phase, the code representations generated by the PM2-CNN may not be optimal.",
    "Therefore, we design a detection model based on pre-trained CodeT5+ to capture semantic features and generate code representations.",
    "Moreover, collecting accurate descriptive documents for each program is challenging (as pointed out by the ablation study in PM2-CNN) [12].",
    "Thus, in our research, instead of using descriptive documents, we opt for expert metrics, which are easier to collect."
  ]
}